#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/http-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "By default, the following list of media types is compressed: `text/html`, `text/plain`, `text/xml`, `text/css`, `text/javascript`, `application/javascript`, `application/json`, `application/graphql+json` and `application/xhtml+xml`."
msgstr "Por padrĂŁo, a seguinte lista de tipos de mĂ­dia Ă© compactada: `text/html` , `text/plain` , `text/xml` , `text/css` , `text/javascript` , `application/javascript` , `application/json` , `application/graphql+json` e `application/xhtml+xml` ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/http-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
